Enable Article Recommendations

To get started, turn on Einstein Article Recommendations.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions.
USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
Customize Application
Salesforce Knowledge enabled

From Setup, enter Einstein Article Recommendations, and then select it.
Review Terms, accept them, and click Try Einstein.
Click the toggle to turn on Einstein Article Recommendations.

Select Languages and Fields for Your Article Recommendation Model
